T
T(\alpha X + \beta Y) = \alpha T(X) + \beta T(Y), \tag{1}
\alpha, \beta \in R
X, Y \in R^{n \times n}
T(\alpha X + \beta Y) = B(\alpha X + \beta Y)B = B(\alpha X)B + B(\beta Y)B = \alpha BXB + \beta BYB = \alpha T(X) + \beta T(Y); \tag{2}
